{"tid":2516693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加州迪士尼白雪公主園區被指教壞小孩　美媒：王子不應隨意親吻公主","createTime":"2021-05-04T22:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T22:36:35.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d10049bf3521eab47bc0e77cbbe864bb00a1d5b8","tid":2516693,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T22:25:04.000Z","msg":"加州迪士尼樂園停業超過一年後，上周五終於重新開放，卻馬上接到投訴。投訴原因並非防疫措施不足，而是在新園區設施「Snow White&rsquo;s Enchanted Wish」內，重現王子親吻白雪公主一幕，惹來舊金山新聞網站「SF Gate」記者投訴指，王子沒有得到公主允許而親吻對方是「教壞小孩」。<br />\n<br />\n為增加園區吸引力，加州迪士尼樂園在閉園期間，翻新白雪公主園區，加入新的音效和視覺效果，重新呈現白雪公主故事場景，並以王子親吻白雪公主作結尾。<br />\n<br />\n這經典一幕惹來「SF Gate」旅遊版記者Katie Dowd和Julie Tremaine不滿。她們在文中批評，有關畫面不怡當，因為王子在未經白雪公主許可下，趁其昏迷而親吻她，不是真愛表現，「我們不是都已經同意，一些早期的迪士尼電影內容不恰當嗎？我們不是都在教導孩子，要在雙方同意才可以親吻別人嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n她批評，「很難理解迪士尼樂園在2021年，仍然把男性可以這些對待女性的守舊想法，加入園內，特別是公司已經移除了Jungle Cruise和Splash Mountain這些有問題場景」。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210505/3COL6FBR2FBDBPZW3UXKM2HPIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210505%2F3COL6FBR2FBDBPZW3UXKM2HPIY%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=f380c61e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210505%2F3COL6FBR2FBDBPZW3UXKM2HPIY%2F&h=4f4a30ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210505/3COL6FBR2FBDBPZW3UXKM2HPIY/</a>"},{"pid":"ba9aabc00ea12e04122b0e3afb60e308f3e86f0b","tid":2516693,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T22:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原罪"},{"pid":"38f4bf68b9a36f305ab59c96391de90513d7fa4d","tid":2516693,"uid":263191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9aabc00ea12e04122b0e3afb60e308f3e86f0b","tid":2516693,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T22:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa